00:10:54.180 --> 00:11:01.879
Those who only belong to the Kingdom of God
have achieved something.

00:11:01.879 --> 00:11:09.339
The rest of them are useless people, just
finding some way to fight each other, to denounce

00:11:09.339 --> 00:11:15.639
