00:11:15.639 --> 00:11:24.610
If somebody just puts a pin into it the whole
balloon will collapse.

00:11:24.610 --> 00:11:32.319
Now the worst of all is jealousy, and that
is among Indians, Indians are very big jealous

00:11:32.319 --> 00:11:34.079
pots.

00:11:34.079 --> 00:11:40.050
Specially the Indians who are again in the
