I said, “But it’s not Mine, that’s My
husband’s, you see.”

00:12:26.629 --> 00:12:30.819
What is there to be jealous because I’m
sitting in a Mercedes car.

00:12:30.819 --> 00:12:37.510
I mean, this is being a very stupid, nonsensical
thing but still I can’t believe you can

00:12:37.510 --> 00:12:44.999
be jealous of somebody because he has a Mercedes
car, what does it matter?

00:12:44.999 --> 00:12:53.069
To Me, it’s a foreign idea absolutely, I
can’t understand.

00:12:53.069 --> 00:12:56.790
But there are stupid and stupid things like
that.

00:12:56.790 --> 00:13:15.010
I can only understand one jealousy, that is
between husband and wife, little bit.

00:13:17.910 --> 00:13:34.180
Then the fifth thing that He asked us to kill
is the attachment, very important, “This

00:13:34.180 --> 00:13:36.160
is my child, this is my…”

00:13:36.160 --> 00:13:42.790
This is Indian also, more Indian, “This
is my cousin, this is my brother, this is

00:13:42.790 --> 00:13:45.269
my fiancé, this is my wife.”

00:13:45.269 --> 00:13:54.129
Also in the West, the other way round is that
they do not care for their children.

00:13:54.129 --> 00:13:57.610
They do not care for their mothers, they do
not care for their fathers.

00:13:57.610 --> 00:14:06.589
They do not care for anyone whatsoever, but
for themselves.

00:14:06.589 --> 00:14:11.309
That comes from the last one, is called as
the greed.

00:14:11.309 --> 00:14:18.699
Now when you have greed, you don’t care
for anybody, you just want to have everything,

00:14:18.699 --> 00:14:22.199
from another person.

00:14:22.199 --> 00:14:26.929
You want to grab another person of everything.

00:14:26.929 --> 00:14:32.579
Whatever another person has, you want to have
it.

00:14:32.579 --> 00:14:36.369
But when you don’t want to have it everybody
wants to give you it, that’s My case.

00:14:36.369 --> 00:14:43.299
I’m very afraid to say even that, “This
is nice,” because immediately tomorrow I’ll

00:14:43.299 --> 00:14:53.389
find it in My house.

00:14:53.389 --> 00:14:58.649
So this greed is the one which has done such
a harm to the whole world.

00:14:58.649 --> 00:15:04.649
People have gone into great dominations on
other countries, for what?

00:15:04.649 --> 00:15:08.380
For these diamonds and nonsensical things
like that?

00:15:08.380 --> 00:15:13.859
They have ruined their own lives, the progenies
