00:15:13.859 --> 00:15:21.069
All their cunning they have used to ruin so
many nations just to put them one against

00:15:21.069 --> 00:15:27.160
another, creating problems, doing all kinds
of intrique.

00:15:27.160 --> 00:15:28.459
Just for what?

00:15:28.459 --> 00:15:37.660
For greed which is absolutely like cancer,
doesn’t allow anybody else to exist.

00:15:37.660 --> 00:15:42.439
And then you start eating yourself out.

00:15:42.439 --> 00:15:46.529
It’s a disease, I think, greed.

00:15:46.529 --> 00:15:55.089
And with that goes the miserliness; people
become miserly.

00:15:55.089 --> 00:15:57.949
Then where does this greed end up.

00:15:57.949 --> 00:16:05.169
After all the money that accumulates or things
that accumulate in your house, what happens

00:16:05.169 --> 00:16:07.279
to them?

00:16:07.279 --> 00:16:13.589
You want to use them.

00:16:13.589 --> 00:16:17.009
What’s the matter with this one?

00:16:17.009 --> 00:16:24.100
Try to be, not to be, I’ve told, otherwise
I’ll ask you to go out, all right?

00:16:24.100 --> 00:16:25.100
Concentrate.

00:16:25.100 --> 00:16:32.579
So what happens to the people who are greedy?

00:16:32.579 --> 00:16:39.730
They become miserly, they can’t enjoy life,
they cannot spend money because the greatest

00:16:39.730 --> 00:16:44.319
joy is in giving things to others, no doubt
about it.

00:16:44.319 --> 00:16:51.239
And they cannot give any joy to anyone, they
cannot create anything for the future progeny

00:16:51.239 --> 00:16:52.919
to see.

00:16:52.919 --> 00:16:54.419
So what happens to them?

00:16:54.419 --> 00:16:59.689
Their children when they come in they become
wastrel, waste.

00:16:59.689 --> 00:17:08.910
They waste all of them, they lead a wasteful
life, they get into wrong things, and ruin

00:17:08.910 --> 00:17:09.910
themselves.

00:17:09.910 --> 00:17:13.320
So their children who are born become miserly.

00:17:13.320 --> 00:17:16.579
So the vicious circle starts moving.

00:17:16.579 --> 00:17:29.260
He has said, “Kill all of them, these are
your six enemies.”

